      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably preserved motorcar, currently maintained in showroom condition. This vehicle exemplifies automotive excellence, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains in its original, pristine state. Meticulously serviced and stored in a climate-controlled environment, this example offers a level of refinement and mechanical integrity that will satisfy the most discerning collector. Every detail, from the tactile response of the switchgear to the luster of the paintwork, confirms its status as a premier specimen of the marque.",
      "price": 48500.0,
