    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this absolute beauty. Honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014it's in flawless shape and has been my absolute pride and joy. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and staying on top of every single service. It drives like a dream and still has that new-car feel! I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
