      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a superlative 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, a definitive 996.2 wide-body featuring the 3.6L flat-six power plant with VarioCam Plus valve timing. This example is mechanically pristine, with the critical IMS bearing retrofit already completed and bore-scoping verified. The 6-speed G96/31 manual transmission offers crisp, short-throw engagement, sending power through a viscous-coupling AWD system. The chassis is equipped with the M030 sport suspension and four-piston Brembo monoblock calipers over cross-drilled rotors, providing exceptional thermal management and stopping power. The original paint retains a deep, mirror-like finish, and the undercarriage shows no signs of oxidation or fluid seepage. This is a turn-key, investment-grade enthusiast's machine with a comprehensive service dossier.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
